'''Lí Hiông-làn''' ({{bd|1920-ngièn|2-ngie̍t 12-ngit|2014-ngièn|9-ngie̍t 7-ngit|catIdx=L李}}), chhut-se miàng '''Yamaguchi Yoshiko''' ({{jpn|j=山口 淑子|hg=やまぐち よしこ|rm=}}), thi-ngi-kói kiet-fûn heu fu-sit miàng '''Ōtaka Yoshiko'''({{jpn|j=大鷹淑子|hg=おおたかよしこ|rm=}}), [[Ngit-pún-ngìn]], ku-hiông [[Ngit-pún]] [[Saga-yen]] [[Kishima-khiùn]] Kitagata-chhûn (liá-ha [[Saga-yen]] [[Takeo-sṳ]] Kitagata-thín), chhut-se yî [[Chûng-fà Mìn-koet]] [[Fung-thiên-sén]] [[Fung-thiên-sṳ]] Pet-yên-thòi (liá-ha [[Liâu-nèn-sén]] [[Tên-thap-sṳ]]), su-ko chang-sṳt [[sî-yòng]] [[sâng-lo̍k]] kau-yuk, he [[sú-chhìn ńg-kô-yîm]], chhai-hàng mî-sâng chhong-fap, he tông-sṳ̀ chhêu tî-miàng ke kô-sú, thien-yáng yên-yèn, heu tâm-ngim [[Ngit-pún chhâm-ngi-yen]] [[chhâm-ngi-yèn]]. 2014-ngièn 9-ngie̍t 7-ngit, yîn [[sîm-chhong sôi-khe̍t]] chhai kâ tú ko-sṳ̂n, hióng ngièn 94-se<ref>{{cite news | title = 唱紅夜來香李香蘭病逝| publisher = [[中央社]] | url = http: //www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201409140101-1.aspx | date = 2014-09-14 | accessdate = 2014-09-14 | language = zh-tw}}</ref><ref> {{cite news | title = 山口淑子さん死去「李香蘭」の名前で活躍| publisher = [[日本放送協會|NHK]] | url = http://www3.nhk.or.jp/news/html/20140914 /k10014592341000.html | date = 2014-09-14 | accessdate = 2014-09-14 | language = ja}}</ref>.
